query:
SELECT id, householdId, name, sharedHouseholdIds, 
  CASE 
    WHEN sharedHouseholdIds IS NULL THEN 'NULL'
    WHEN JSON_VALID(sharedHouseholdIds) = 0 THEN 'INVALID_JSON'
    ELSE JSON_TYPE(sharedHouseholdIds)
  END as dataType
FROM tasks 
WHERE sharedHouseholdIds IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 20
